Package: RTides
Type: Package
Title: Harmonic tidal analysis and prediction
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Cam", "Appel", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "cam@appel.co.uk")
Description: Harmonic tidal analysis and prediction using astronomical
    arguments and nodal corrections per Schureman, ported from the Python
    'Pytides' project.
